    <item>
      <title>苹果推动将人工智能融入设备的努力将需要数年时间才能获得回报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-06-11/will-apple-intelligence-features-boost-iphone-sales-it-may-take-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，苹果终于公布了其人工智能成果，同时对其操作系统进行了小幅升级。但新的 Apple Intelligence 功能可能不会对今年的 iPhone 销量产生太大推动作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-06-11/will-apple-intelligence-features-boost-iphone-sales-it-may-take-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 12:00:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
